  "content": "# Get User Setting\n\nRetrieve the parameters of a User Setting.\n\n## Endpoint\n\n`GET /users/settings/{setting_name}/get`",
  "summary": "Get User Setting",
  "source": "openapi.json",
  "code_examples": [
    {
